    {
      "id": "6090ec23aff09e00003d13ae",
      "text": " <comment>",
      "created": 1241967600,
      "updated": 1241967600,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec23aff09e00003d13af",
      "text": " <username>nagakura_eil</username>",
      "created": 1241967600,
      "updated": 1241967600,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec23aff09e00003d13b0",
      "text": " <body>まわすプレイする人が多かったら、常に2分の1ちょっとの確率で勝負する人のところに自然とカードが集まって虫を押し付けられて不利なのでは？？</body>",
      "created": 1241967600,
      "updated": 1241967600,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec23aff09e00003d13b1",
      "text": " <timestamp>1242059808</timestamp>",
      "created": 1241967600,
      "updated": 1241967600,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec23aff09e00003d13b2",
